    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "The system allows users to search for other users by selecting a price range as a filter.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall allow users to search for other users by selecting a price range as a filter."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "After the user selects a filter, the system displays matching users based on the chosen criteria.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall display matching users based on the chosen criteria after the user selects a filter."
    }
  ]
}
```
